text: Guillermo Bruno Victorino Giribaldi was a footballer from Curaçao. Giribaldi competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics. He was born on 17 May 1929.Guillermo Giribaldi == References == Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Curaçao footballers Category:Curaçao Olympians
